      "segmentName": "Equipment Details Loop",
      "usage": "M",
      "maxRepeat": 1,
      "isLoopStart": true,
      "purpose": "Loop containing equipment information. Owlery always sends N702 as 000000 because Owlery never controls or has knowledge about the equipment numbers during tender; the stable placeholder keeps the segment structure consistent without implying an assigned unit.",
